  15 Nov 2004; Gustavo Zacarias <gustavoz@gentoo.org> plib-1.8.3.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc

  21 Oct 2004; Seemant Kulleen <seemant@gentoo.org> -plib-1.4.2-r1.ebuild,
  plib-1.8.3.ebuild:
  move 1.8.3 to stable x86 and remove outdated 1.4.2-r1. This is required for
  moving flighgear-0.9.4 to stable

  02 Oct 2004; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org> plib-1.8.3.ebuild:
  Marked ppc, this version works with gcc3.4

  21 Jun 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> plib-1.8.2.ebuild:
  clean older version

  13 May 2004; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  add metadata for games herd since plib is mostly used for games

